              "id": "s1",
              "text_en": "Drag the mass slider and watch what happens."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2",
              "text_en": "Increase the mass and the weight arrow grows. Decrease it and the arrow shrinks."
            },
            {
              "id": "s3",
              "text_en": "The relationship is linear — double the mass, double the weight. Always."
            },
            {
              "id": "s4",
              "text_en": "And this force is never switched off. As long as Earth exists, its field exists, and so does your weight."
            }
          ]
